graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        Controller[Controller Manager<br/>Reconciles ModelRegistry CRs]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Validates/Mutates CRs]
        Controller -->|uses| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        MRv1beta1[ModelRegistry CR v1beta1<br/>Current API]
        MRv1alpha1[ModelRegistry CR v1alpha1<br/>Deprecated]
    end

    subgraph "Per-Instance Deployment"
        RESTContainer[REST Container<br/>Model Registry API]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>OpenShift Authentication]
        RESTContainer -.->|sidecar| OAuthProxy
    end

    subgraph "Kubernetes Resources Created"
        Deployment["Deployment<br/>(name)"]
        Service["Service<br/>(name)"]
        Route["OpenShift Route<br/>(name)"]
        SA["ServiceAccount<br/>(name)"]
        Roles["Roles & RoleBindings"]
        NetPol["NetworkPolicy<br/>(name)-https-route"]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| MRv1beta1
    User -->|creates| MRv1alpha1
    MRv1beta1 -->|watched by| Controller
    MRv1alpha1 -->|watched by| Controller
    Controller -->|creates| Deployment
    Controller -->|creates| Service
    Controller -->|creates| Route
    Controller -->|creates| SA
    Controller -->|creates| Roles
    Controller -->|creates| NetPol

    Deployment -->|contains| RESTContainer
    Deployment -->|contains| OAuthProxy

    RESTContainer -->|connects to| PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL<br/>ML Metadata Storage)]
    RESTContainer -->|connects to| MySQL[(MySQL<br/>Alternative Storage)]

    OAuthProxy -->|validates tokens| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
    Service -->|exposes| RESTContainer
    Service -->|exposes| OAuthProxy
    Route -->|routes to| Service

    Controller -->|integrates| Platform[opendatahub-operator<br/>Platform Component]
    Controller -->|monitored by| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MRv1beta1 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MRv1alpha1 fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style RESTContainer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PostgreSQL fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MySQL fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthServer fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Platform fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
